name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-005: It is the Road
description: Chapter 1, panel 5. When a cowboy asks for clarification, a guide may elaborate. To understand love and cowboy love, one must have lived a thousand lives in a single lifetime. The road is a structure that reaches through time as well as space. A cowboy has to understand. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
